title: "PACE: Pattern for Agentic Conversational Experience"
abstract: >
  PACE is a design framework for guide-first interfaces where AI leads users 
  through conversation rather than traditional navigation. The acronym works 
  on two levels: as "Pattern for Agentic Conversational Experience" (the what) 
  and as four behavioral principlesâ€”Proactive, Adaptive, Contextual, Efficient 
  (the how). PACE inverts the traditional browse-and-hunt paradigm, placing 
  an AI guide at the center of the user experience.
